document_data.name: East Market Street
document_data.mainbody: '''East Market Street''' was a small branched street found in the city of [[Westgate]].
document_data.Location: East Market Street was found in the south section of the city. It connected with [[Silverpiece Way]] and [[Westgate Market Street]] then branched once before ending at the city's perimeter wall. A city watch barracks was located on East Market Street.
